The '''Void Demons''' were a [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] group stationed at a [[Void Demon pirate base|pirate base]] on the [[Planetoid/Legends|planetoid]] [[Isen IV]] in the [[Isen system/Legends|Isen system]]. They were known to chase [[Spacer/Legends|spacers]] across [[Hyperspace route/Legends|hyperlanes]].

During the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], the Void Demons were led by [[Abav Ghart]].<ref name="PoG1">''[[Planets of the Galaxy, Volume One]]''</ref>

